"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"因為個老豆奶完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c6d9aed1c1df4c57b5e833e1c791ba94d1b041","tid":1165794,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"指從小在一個非常保守的宗教傳統家庭長大，其父母認為婚前不可有性行為。<br />\n物極必反呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c044f0dc1a22642b81d73dedd8db3d31fd26bd73","tid":1165794,"uid":165187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b52db8db93a9ec1fc0db0aa2d87ecb6a1e1c81","tid":1165794,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"其實係個女保護爸爸救咗個家"}]}